Subject: crypto: octeontx2 - add LF reset on queue disable
Patch-mainline: v6.8-rc1
Git-commit: cac482f2418bf0d140ed89650dbb0413e9fe1f58
References: jsc#PED-11318

CPT LF must be reset and follow CPT LF disable sequence
suggested by HW team, when driver exits.
This patch adds code for the same.

